Teaching + Learning Lab
Open Learning
MIT is pioneering new ways of teaching and learning, on our campus and around the world, by inventing and leveraging digital technologies.
MITx
, the Institute’s portfolio of massively open online courses, offers flexible access to a range of interactive courses developed and taught by instructors from MIT. Another MIT innovation — the
MicroMasters
credential — is increasingly recognized by industry leaders hiring new talent. And MIT’s original digital learning option,
OpenCourseWare
, continues to offer teachers and learners worldwide the materials for more than 2,450 MIT courses, freely available online.
